                "display_name": "Rahul",
                "accept_rate": 60
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1354687253,
            "creation_date": 1354687253,
            "body": "<p>java.awt.* can not be resolved in android as java.awt.* contains native code. These native code needs to be supported by android separately. So far, it is not done.<\/p>\n\n<p>However, you can use android.graphics, android's graphics library.<\/p>\n\n<p>More information available at :\n<a href=\"http://developer.android.com/reference/android/graphics/package-summary.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://developer.android.com/reference/android/graphics/package-summary.html<\/a><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 13717244,
            "question_id": 13709030
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/vw9qZ.png?s=256",
                "account_id": 1069432,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 1069068,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1069068/raghav-sood",
                "reputation": 82629,
                "display_name": "Raghav Sood",
                "accept_rate": 80
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1354644750,
            "creation_date": 1354644750,
            "body": "<p>These imports cannot be resolved on Android.<\/p>\n\n<p>While Android has a lot of classes that the standard Java Development Kit does, it implements its own UI system. Due to this, awt is not included in Android.<\/p>\n\n<p>However, <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/awt-android-compat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">attempts<\/a> have been made at porting parts of awt to Android. I haven't tried out the project personally, so I can't say if it meets your requirements.<\/p>\n\n<p>You could also look into JavaCV and OpenCV for image processing on Android.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 13709236,
            "question_id": 13709030
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/ae8a750804fe907a7557f9459bd8c582?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
                "account_id": 11843640,
                "user_type": "registered",
